CatDescriptText: Two men pose for a photograph in a jazz club.  In the background there are images of jazz musicians in frames.  The man on the left is wearing a grey double-breasted suit with a white collared shirt and a patterned tie.  The man on the right is wearing a double-breasted grey pin-striped suit with a white handkerchief, a white collared shirt, and a patterned tie.
TitMainTitle: Two men wearing double breasted suits, one wearing moustache, standing in theatre lobby with "Coming Attractions" sign in background
